magazine_service

Class PayingCustomer

  • java.lang.Object
    • magazine_service.Customer
      • magazine_service.PayingCustomer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PayingCustomer
extends Customer
implements java.io.Serializable
    The PayingCustomer class represents a paying customer in the magazine service. It extends the Customer class and includes information about the payment method and associated customers.
    See Also:
